{"tid":2418074,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【7.7九龍遊行】拍照被指是女警遭包圍　事主被揭曾襲警及意圖縱火被判感化　","createTime":"2021-02-22T10:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T11:39:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fa9be66c14116ffd1023b2fba315f7f55357bf2f","tid":2418074,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:43:40.000Z","msg":"2019 年 7 月 7 日九龍區反修例遊行後，有女子疑被誤當便衣警遭包圍。2 男 1 女被控一項非法禁錮及非法集結罪，包括一名女教師，其中一名男子另被控非禮。三人否認控罪，案件今 (22 日) 於區域法院開審，事主下午接受辯方盤問期間，承認她曾因違反檢疫令而被判囚兩周，以及曾經醉酒襲擊休班女警及意圖縱火，被判感化。案情指事主當時表示「我見到差人就要打」。<br />\n<br />\n控方下午繼續播放涉案片段， 獲准於屏風後作供的事主 X 指自己當時覺得「好無助」及被侵犯，覺得被人控制全身，很難移動，「因為成身都比人拉住」。片段又顯示，事主曾一度大叫「強姦」，又見到一名白衣男子用雙手從後伸進事主的腋下。事主表示她當時感到不舒服及厭惡，曾嘗試撥開對方的手。<br />\n<br />\n代表首被告的大律師姚本成盤問事主 X 時指，她事發期間並沒表示自己被非禮，事後亦沒有向警方提出。事主確認，但強調她曾大叫「強姦」。 她又指，事發後沒有即時報警，回家後「成晚無訓」。她翌日下午睡醒後，發現社交傳媒有很多相關事件的報道，令她決定報警，因「我覺得我可能唔安全，自己一個喺香港」。<br />\n<br />\n事主 X 又於辯方盤問下承認，曾因違反檢疫令而被判囚兩周，又承認她早前醉酒後，曾襲擊一名休班女警及意圖縱火。X 表示她與該休班女警相識，因「飲大咗」而犯案。辯方指相關案情指 X 襲擊對方時曾指「我見到差人就要打」。X 則表示「聽講係咁」，解釋相關案情是由證人提出，她當時因為醉酒，記不起曾說過相關內容。案件明天繼續。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/7-7%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E6%8B%8D%E7%85%A7%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%98%AF%E5%A5%B3%E8%AD%A6%E9%81%AD%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D-%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%BB%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%AD%E6%9B%BE%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E5%A5%B3%E8%AD%A6-%E7%A8%B1-%E6%88%91%E8%A6%8B%E5%88%B0%E5%B7%AE%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%B1%E8%A6%81%E6%89%93/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F7-7%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E6%258B%258D%25E7%2585%25A7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%258C%2585%25E5%259C%258D-%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258F%25AD%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E7%25A8%25B1-%25E6%2588%2591%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%2589%2593%2F&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XnwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=36d7903b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F7-7%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E6%258B%258D%25E7%2585%25A7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%258C%2585%25E5%259C%258D-%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258F%25AD%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E7%25A8%25B1-%25E6%2588%2591%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%2589%2593%2F&h=b21f5cd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/7-7%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E6%8B%8D%E7%85%A7%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%98%AF%E5%A5%B3%E8%AD%A6%E9%81%AD%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D-%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%BB%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%AD%E6%9B%BE%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E5%A5%B3%E8%AD%A6-%E7%A8%B1-%E6%88%91%E8%A6%8B%E5%88%B0%E5%B7%AE%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%B1%E8%A6%81%E6%89%93/</a>"},{"pid":"a3f8e4f64cbc4390813b4ab2ae539513a9f40b8c","tid":2418074,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbdc7862189ea9d33b7fa5f42ab6016af0531bd4","tid":2418074,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3f8e4f64cbc4390813b4ab2ae539513a9f40b8c","tid":2418074,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor